<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="email.css" />

    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <title>Email</title>
    <style>
        * {
            font-family: "Roboto", sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            background-color: #f6f3f3;
        }

        span {
            width: 60%;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            background-color: #ffff;
            padding: 50px 0px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 10px;
            -webkit-box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 4px -1px rgba(66, 68, 90, 1);
            -moz-box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 4px -1px rgba(66, 68, 90, 1);
            box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 4px -1px rgba(66, 68, 90, 1);
        }

        h3 {
            font-size: 20px;
            line-height: 30px;
            height: 40px;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 17px;
            line-height: 25px;
        }

        button {
            padding: 15px 40px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            background-color: #03a9f4;
            border-color: transparent;
            font-size: 17px;
            color: #fff;
        }

        @media screen and (width <=425px) {
            span {
                width: 95%;
                padding: 50px 0px;
                text-align: center;
                border-radius: 10px;
                -webkit-box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 4px -1px rgba(66, 68, 90, 1);
                -moz-box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 4px -1px rgba(66, 68, 90, 1);
                box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 4px -1px rgba(66, 68, 90, 1);
            }

            h3 {
                font-size: 15px;
            }

            p {
                font-size: 15px;
                line-height: 25px;
                width: 250px;
            }

            button {
                padding: 10px 15px;
                border-radius: 5px;
                background-color: #03a9f4;
                border-color: transparent;
                font-size: 15px;
                color: #fff;
            }
        }

        @media screen and (width <=375px) {
            span {
                width: 95%;
                padding: 50px 0px;
                text-align: center;
                border-radius: 10px;
                -webkit-box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 4px -1px rgba(66, 68, 90, 1);
                -moz-box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 4px -1px rgba(66, 68, 90, 1);
                box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 4px -1px rgba(66, 68, 90, 1);
            }

            h3 {
                font-size: 15px;
            }

            p {
                font-size: 15px;
                line-height: 25px;
                width: 250px;
            }

            button {
                padding: 10px 15px;
                border-radius: 5px;
                background-color: #03a9f4;
                border-color: transparent;
                font-size: 15px;
                color: #fff;
            }
        }

        @media screen and (width <=320px) {
            span {
                width: 95%;
                padding: 50px 0px;
                text-align: center;
                border-radius: 10px;
                -webkit-box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 4px -1px rgba(66, 68, 90, 1);
                -moz-box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 4px -1px rgba(66, 68, 90, 1);
                box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 4px -1px rgba(66, 68, 90, 1);
            }

            h3 {
                font-size: 13px;
            }

            p {
                font-size: 13px;
                line-height: 25px;
                width: 250px;
            }

            button {
                padding: 10px 15px;
                border-radius: 5px;
                background-color: #03a9f4;
                border-color: transparent;
                font-size: 13px;
                color: #fff;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <h1>Password reset</h1>
    <span>
        <h3>Someone requested that the passowrd be<br /> reset for the following account:</h3>
        <p>To reset your password, visit the following address:</p>
        <a href="https://marco-lyart.vercel.app/#/change.password/{{url}}">
            <button>Click here to reset your password</button>
        </a>
        <p>If it was a mistake, ignore this email and help us secure your account.</p>
    </span>
</body>

</html>